NOTES:


Well firstly the source......some very nice 1080p files,but like all cams they have issues.
Issues with this was that the colours seem to have a green hue,filmed at a angle and the dark scenes
were very dark ( like that in the cinema though ).
So we had to use the perspective filter to pull it straight and then crop all unwanted borders.Then from there
we changed the RGB eq to balance the colours out better.....also used brightness,contrast,heavy denoiser,sharpness filters.
Got to pre warn you,so hope you read before you download  the dark scenes are still very dark and cranking up the brightness
anymore you lose other details as you create hotspots.
Audio we have to clean up by using a hiss removal and changing the EQ and then we synced it to our encode.

Anyway enjoy this pretty dam good TS
